{"tid":1521794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警被斬單嘢令我諗起希特拉","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:03.000Z","uid":260766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d02541dc0b74c70ef9955e5761aefbdda91b77d","tid":1521794,"uid":260766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"當年德國納粹燒完個國會後，希特拉順勢搞埋<br />\n《國會縱火法令》，廢除咗《魏瑪憲法》有關保證人身自由嘅條款，結果&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n到今日香港黑警俾人斬完就開始秋後算帳&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nsorry, 係我垃圾，今日老母連屋企門口都唔俾我出，仲話一出門口就要跟蹤我喎(全家3個藍，得我一個係黃)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家諗緊好唔好自己課金租屋住，唔租就永遠失去免於恐懼嘅自由租完我又冇咩錢剩&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b750c9500751452b11a0748a6691bdb9ad365692","tid":1521794,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"1845 現場手足報料：「啱啱試過含酒精濕紙巾可抹走顏色水」<br />\n幫忙廣傳"},{"pid":"672b8917bc3c36b054a120c9a70e322965a26b7b","tid":1521794,"uid":16372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"出你一個多3個 谷人數"},{"pid":"54ac50d66b25644eafb5a3ed7eb8b890ea2d0269","tid":1521794,"uid":260766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b750c9500751452b11a0748a6691bdb9ad365692","tid":1521794,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"1845 現場手足報料：「啱啱試過含酒精濕紙巾可抹走顏色水」<br />\n幫忙廣傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"廣傳咗，可以再傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1d1740d1427ad9bd63dab7f73797